column5: Nice promo for the upcoming Fishing for Tyler Event on 14th Feb and for the OFC community site on "A" news this morning...  I felt sorry for Lou from the Simcoe Bait And Tackle store...fished real hard for the three hours but ...NADA...oh well...that's fishin'...
Yes, congrats Maureen, that was awesome.  I watched it all morning as I got ready for work.  You looked nervous LOL.  I would have been the same.  But you did a fantastic job  Joey

Thanks Norm and Joey, ya I was a little nervous....I guess a career in TV is not for me   Thanks also to Dave (tinbanger) who brought us coffee, and Karl and Mark from Extreme Angler TV for helping out, as well as misfish for his support.  Maureen
Did anyone get a copy of it?
great job Maureen I am sure you did us all proud. If someone can put a link to the piece it sure would be a nice thing for us stuck alittle further South.....  Thanks  Art

Theres no fish where he was. Theres no fish in Simcoe.LOL  Yes Mo great job. Nice chatting and talking with Karl and Mark. I guess the guy didnt want to talk to me.LOL THANK GAWD.  Oh and Dave,that coffee is still working. I cant seem to calm down. Triple expresso
great job Maureen .. This years 'Fishing for Tyler' outta be a record breaker.  And Brian I don't think it was the coffee  TB
